of strangling the life

00:00:05.271 --> 00:00:08.408
out of Victor's body
or having him get hit by a train

00:00:08.441 --> 00:00:10.777
or drowning in a bath
of his own brandy vomit,

00:00:10.810 --> 00:00:14.113
I think it's kinder to have him
arrested for battery.

00:00:14.146 --> 00:00:16.516
Sorry about this, Victor,
but you're going to jail.

00:00:23.789 --> 00:00:25.525
Ah!

00:00:25.558 --> 00:00:27.093
[grunts]

00:00:27.126 --> 00:00:29.462 align:start position:0%
[crying]

00:00:29.495 --> 00:00:33.466 size:81% position:41%
