00:00:33.499 --> 00:00:35.268 align:end position:100%
I'm so sorry
for your pain, ma'am.

00:00:35.301 --> 00:00:38.137 align:end position:100%
Ay, you'll tell us who the black
fella was who did this,

00:00:38.170 --> 00:00:40.406 align:end position:100%
and we'll throw him
in the pokey right quick.

00:00:40.439 --> 00:00:43.609
Oh, no,
it--it was my husband.

00:00:43.642 --> 00:00:45.211
[cries]

00:00:45.244 --> 00:00:47.647 align:start position:0%
Well, that's another
matter entirely.

00:00:47.680 --> 00:00:49.282 align:start size:38% position:63%
Case closed.

00:00:49.315 --> 00:00:51.250
I'm telling you,
I was abused by my husband

00:00:51.283 --> 00:00:53.419
in a manner that only a divorce
would settle.

00:00:53.452 --> 00:00:55.254 align:end position:100%
Well, let me ask
you something, dear.

00:00:55.287 --> 00:00:56.422 align:start size:50% position:50%
Are you a bitch?

00:00:56.455 --> 00:00:57.857
What?

00:00:57.890 --> 00:00:59.625 align:start position:0%
Let's go about this
in a different manner.

00:00:59.658 --> 00:01:02.361 align:start position:0%
Were you menstruating
at the time of the incident?

