Were you riding
the red river?

00:01:04.630 --> 00:01:07.133 align:end position:100%
And do you have
a raspberry bush?

00:01:07.166 --> 00:01:11.037
How dare you?
I was very abused!

00:01:11.070 --> 00:01:12.472 align:start position:0%
Looks to me like
you walked into a door.

00:01:12.505 --> 00:01:14.107
[gasps]

00:01:14.140 --> 00:01:15.374
